{"data":[{"date":"07:13 12/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea: M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/du-am-huddersfield-03-chelsea-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1edbi ngay c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V The Blues c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Khi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Kante v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Blues r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ee9 ngh\u0129 m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n Kepa chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb rung l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01a1i. V\u00e0 sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 1 b\u00e0n, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Chelsea, h\u1ecd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Du-am-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-Man-ra-mat-hoan-hao-cua-Sarri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 2, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi Chelsea n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. B\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a &ldquo;t\u00e2n binh&rdquo; Eden Hazard.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Kante, Hazard, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng nh\u01b0 Pedro, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh Jorginho hay th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Kepa Arrizabalaga &ndash; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London t\u1ea1o ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pedro Hazard\" title=\"Pedro Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/ped.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pedro v\u00e0 Hazard t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi Sarriball</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng khen nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Blues. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Kepa tuy kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 23 tu\u1ed5i, khi anh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng cho nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, Marcos Alonso d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi, khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00e2ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger &ndash; Luiz, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri trao ni\u1ec1m tin trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao vai tr\u00f2 l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec John Stones th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong Pep-team, David Luiz s\u1edf h\u1eefu 93 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 &ldquo;vua chuy\u1ec1n&rdquo; Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/chel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Luiz (30) trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, N&rsquo;Golo Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1ec7ch c\u00e1nh, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 lo nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hi\u1ebfm hoi Kante ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0&hellip; 1, 1 v\u00e0 1. Nh\u01b0ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri, Kante \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Sarriball, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho. Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield, nh\u01b0ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o t\u00e2n binh 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Jorginho th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u? \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a &ldquo;l\u00ean s\u00f3ng&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 trong d\u01b0 \u00e2m Huddersfield vs Chelsea, b\u1edfi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Sarriball v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Pre