n m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sandhausen vs Hamburg 18h30 ng\u00e0y 128 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sandhausen vs Hamburg 18h30 ng\u00e0y 128 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Sandhausen-vs-Hamburg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sandhausen vs Hamburg</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Sandhausen vs Hamburg: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u201cra m\u1eaft\u201d gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c, Hamburg (xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Bundesliga) \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn khi thua tr\u1eafng 3 b\u00e0n ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Christian Titz thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt v\u1edd, tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 h\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1eafn n\u00f3t h\u01a1n, Hamburg c\u00f2n thua \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Hamburg trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n BWT-Stadion am Hardtwald c\u1ee7a Sandhausen. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Hamburg. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Die Rothosen ch\u1ec9 2 l\u1ea7n ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba Volksparkstadion (h\u00f2a 3, thua 12) t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Hamburg ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Bundesliga 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Titz ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 quen thu\u1ed9c Bundesliga.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2264","checkdouble":"194292"},{"date":"08:38 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 12/8): Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-man-city-22h-ngay-128-khac-biet-o-nen-tang.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb hai tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. D\u1ef1a theo \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Man City c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ch\u1eadp ch\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i 22 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c h\u1eadu n\u01a1i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nUnai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd &ldquo;hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00f3a&rdquo; Arsenal v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4 trong s\u1ed1 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 128) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City (22h ng\u00e0y 128) Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-Arsenal-vs-Man-City-(22h-ngay-128)-Khac-biet-o-nen-ta-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf Premier League kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Lucas Torreira hay Matteo Guendouzi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League, kinh ph\u00ed mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Preview Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1282018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Man City 22h ng\u00e0y 12/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 5 t\u00e2n binh Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng. C\u1ea7n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i test \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Premier League khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi tr\u00f2n 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam Ryiad Mahrez, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Leicester \u0111\u0103ng quang n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a 2015/16. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aguero bo lo co hoi cua Man City\" title=\"Aguero bo lo co hoi cua Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Goc-Man-City-Khi-El-Kun-nhay-mua-duoi-anh-mat-troi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea t\u1ea1i Community Shield c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 The Citizens c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Ederson, David Silva, Kevin De Bruyne ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Vincent Kompany, Nico Otamendi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Guardiola gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m \u0111\u1eabm b\u00ean trong t\u1eebng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Man City. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1eabn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Guardiola mang t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man xanh r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Sterling hay David Silva ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: &ldquo;Pep team&rdquo; b\u00e1o tin d\u1eef cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\n<span>Man City \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 h\u1ecd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Chelsea 0-2 Man City \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 Man City. Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu nguy\u00ean c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 Nacho Montreal v\u00e0 Sead Kolasinac. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 thay h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Ainsley Maitland-Niles v\u1eeba non kinh nghi\u1ec7m, v\u1eeba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m khai th\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00eam ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y. \u1ede c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Man City s\u1ebd quy t\u1ee5, t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Mahrez, ng\u00f4i sao De Bruyne cho t\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker. Ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn cho Maitland-Niles kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kolasinac\" title=\"Kolasinac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/kolasinac-chan-thuong-nghi-10-tuan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Kolasinac v\u00e0 Montreal khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEmery v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Guardiola. \u00d4ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong 10 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y (thua 6, h\u00f2a 4). M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ed3i ngon&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Man City. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd thua tan n\u00e1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Premier League, Arsenal th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 0-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. T\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Arsenal ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nArsenal (4-2-3-1):</strong> 19.Leno - 2.Beller\u00edn, 20.Mustafi, 5.Sokratis, 15.Maitland-Niles - 8.Ramsey, 11.Torreira - 7.Mkhitaryan, 10.Ozil, 14.Aubameyang - 9.Lacazette.<br>\r\n<strong>Man City (4-3-3):</strong> 31.Ederson - 2.Walker, 5.Stones, 14.Laporte, 22.Mendy - 17.Bruyne, 25.Fernandinho, 20.B.Silva - 26.Mahrez, 10.Aguero, 19.Sane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Man City th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Arsenal-vs-Man-City-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2263","checkdouble":"194293"},{"date":"08:38 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. Nh\u01b0ng khi s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Tottenham sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Barca to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma v\u00e0 AC Milan. 3 tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00f4i qua, vi\u1ec7c Blaugrana ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong khi con s\u1ed1 7 b\u00e0n thua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u01a1i g\u1eddn g\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i IC\u00a0Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro, Clement Lenglet v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, do Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n h\u01a1n c\u1ea1nh Lenglet.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Barca lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 s\u01a1 h\u1edf n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Luis Suarez, Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Blaugrana l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00e1c \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Barca ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Lionel Messi. Su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111i, Blaugrana v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Ch\u1ec9 khi c\u00f3 anh, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft Barca v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i xung quanh Messi su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t \u0111i ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Blaugrana \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 138) C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Nhan-dinh-Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3h-ngay-138)-Co-Messi-la-co-tat-ca-hinh-anh-3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Messi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Barcs</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Barca c\u00f3 Messi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Leo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Messi, Suarez r\u1ed3i Coutinho \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ibn Batouta, Ma-R\u1ed1c. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0a Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea5t qu\u00e2n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, x\u00f3a \u0111i nh\u1eefng u \u00e1m t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nSevilla kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSevilla nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Lenglet t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Barca r\u1ed3i Joaquin Correa, Guido Pizarro, David Soria, Juan Munoz v\u00e0 Sergio Rico. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 6 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Ibrahim Amadou (t\u1eeb Lille), Joris Gnagnon (Rennes), Aleix Vidal (Barca), Tomas Vaclik (Basel), Roque Mesa (Swansea) r\u1ed3i Sergi G\u00f3mez (Celta Vigo) n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t nhau t\u1edbi Sevilla. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Pablo Mach\u00edn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 chi 57 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Sevilla vs Barca\" title=\"Preview Sevilla vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Preview-Sevilla-vs-Barca.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca 3h ng\u00e0y 13/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 63,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, vi\u1ec7c thu l\u1eddi t\u1eeb chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho th\u1ea5y t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u201ccon bu\u00f4n\u201d v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac Sevilla \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Europa League v\u1edbi Zalgiris Vilnius \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang 3 ng\u00e0y sau ph\u1ea3i bay t\u1edbi Ma-R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1 Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u th\u1ebf \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Barca. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSevilla (3-4-3):</strong> 13.Vaclik - 24.Gnagnon, 4.Kjaer, 25.Mercado - 16.Navas, 7.Mesa, 10.Banega, 18.Escudero - 17.Sarabia, 9.Ben Yedder, 8.Nolito.<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Stegen - 20.Roberto, 3.Pique, 15.Lenglet, 18.Alba - 14.Coutinho, 5.Busquets, 4.Arthur - 10.Messi, 9.Su\u00e1rez, 26.Malcom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Barcelona th\u1eafng 3-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Sevilla vs Barca\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Sevilla vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/Sevilla-vs-Barca-(3-4-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Sevilla vs Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2262","checkdouble":"194294"},{"date":"21:37 11/08","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alli l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf s\u00e2n St James' Park, anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u1ea5t (2) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Spurs v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 18, Aurier th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, Dele Alli kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o di chuy\u1ec3n tho\u00e1t ra kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m t\u1eeb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Alli mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Tottenham ch\u01b0a thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khi Dele Alli ghi b\u00e0n (32 tr\u1eadn, 26 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 6 h\u00f2a).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 13 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u00e1ng 8 v\u1edbi 898 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 44 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Totteham s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Newcastle v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh, r\u1ea5t may cho Tottenham l\u00e0 Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Dele Alli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jan Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng cung b\u1eadc c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00e1c nhau trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jan Vertonghen tu vui mung, that vong cho den lo lang\" title=\"Jan Vertonghen t\u1eeb vui m\u1eebng, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ebfn lo l\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/213405-jan.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jan Vertonghen t\u1eeb vui m\u1eebng, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ebfn lo l\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 163 tr\u1eadn, Vertonghen m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 2 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Joselu g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Newcastle.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Newcastle d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 85, Jan Vertonghen l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Salomon Rondon c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Vertonghen \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lloris b\u00f3 tay, r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 ngang bay ra ngo\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Vertonghen s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Spurs s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tra t\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u vang l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 15 n\u0103m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Tottenham c\u1ee7a Pochettino. Kinh ph\u00ed x\u00e2y SV\u0110 m\u1edbi qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Spurs ph\u1ea3i th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t chi ti\u00eau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino cung Tottenham co 3 diem dau tien o Ngoai hang Anh 2018/19\" title=\"Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may v\u1edbi Tottenham l\u00e0 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, Dele Alli, Hugo Lloris hay Christian Eriksen.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 8 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i St James' Park. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1 sau 18 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng Spurs \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch song m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd to\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Newcastle kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Dubravka (Sparta Prague), trung v\u1ec7 Fabian Schar (Deportivo), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ki Sung-Yueng (Swansea), Kenedy (Chelsea), ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yoshinori Muto (Mainz) v\u00e0 Salomon Rondon (West Brom).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle khong cho thay su thay doi so voi mua giai truoc\" title=\"Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/new-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Rafa Benitez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNewcastle v\u1eabn d\u1ef1a nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Newcastle \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd m\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2261","checkdouble":"194276"},{"date":"22:17 11/08","title":"H\u1ecd n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Newcastle 1-2 Tottenham?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ho-noi-gi-sau-tran-newcastle-12-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Rafa Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, song Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Spurs \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/ho-noi-gi-sau-tran-newcastle-12-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDele Alli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. H\u00f4m nay, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Alli th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, sau \u0111\u00f3 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rafael Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng Newcastle x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Pochettino t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec Rafa Benitez c\u1ee7a Newcastle l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle khong cho thay su thay doi so voi mua giai truoc\" title=\"Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/new-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng Newcastle x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Newcaste \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t sau khi nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2-1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tottenham gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNewcaste \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng x\u00e0 ngang l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Salomon Rondon, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u00e9m may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Tottenham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2260","checkdouble":"194277"},{"date":"21:56 11/08","title":"Real Madrid 3-1 AC Milan: M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/real-madrid-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt Huddersfield vs Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">802 &ndash; Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League gi\u00e0nh h\u01a1n 800 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (802), v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal (800) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Man United (902).<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Felipe Scolari v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008 (th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Portmouth).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">6 &ndash; Kh\u00f4ng ai s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, v\u1edbi 6/6 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 100%). Kinh ho\u00e0ng hoan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">109 &ndash; Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 109 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 209 tr\u1eadn Premier League. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 69 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 40 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">94 &ndash; \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Jorginho trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong 11 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 &ndash; Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Kante c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi Premier League. Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed7i mua Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2259","checkdouble":"194278"},{"date":"23:29 11/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle 1-2 Tottenham: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-newcastle-12-tottenham-chien-thang-cua-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Spurs mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle, HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Harry Kane \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Lucas Moura, Christian Eriksen v\u00e0 Dele Alli.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle vs Tottenham Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle vs Tottenham Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Du-am-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-Chien-thang-cua-hang-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay, song h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n St James' Park. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, trung phong Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Spurs ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n v\u00e0 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham g\u1ed3m Harry Kane, Lucas Moura, Christian Eriksen v\u00e0 Dele Alli ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, qu\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung phong Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o, Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 tung ra 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane tiep tuc khong ghi ban trong thang 8\" title=\"Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau g\u1ea7n 3 tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Kane l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u00e1ng 8. &ldquo;T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rdquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 14 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi 988 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 46 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8.&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Moura ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, song hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n anh ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c, Moura ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Dembele \u1edf ph\u00fat 68.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDele Alli v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00f2n vai. Alli ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, Eriksen kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Moussa Sissoko v\u00e0 Eric Dier c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Dembele hay Son Heung-Min c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hay c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn sau l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Spurs c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jan Vertonghen mo ty so tu rat som\" title=\"Jan Vertonghen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/232537-jan.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h2>Jan Vertonghen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez v\u00e0 Jan Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u1eeb c\u00fa treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen, Sanchez \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Vertonghen d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 161 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trung v\u1ec7 Jan Vertonghen m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 anh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Swansea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m 2013. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Davinson Sanchez, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 tung ra nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham, anh c\u00f3 3 pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Harry Kane v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez dut diem nhieu nhat ben phia Tottenham\" title=\"Sanchez d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Dele Alli nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Serge Aurier. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Alli ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tottenham-172-194276.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tottenham-172-194276.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle?</span><br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nBen Davies d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tham gia v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o, song c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu dem ve chien thang cho Tottenham truoc Newcastle\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2258","checkdouble":"194280"},{"date":"23:38 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 th\u00e0nh 4-3-3 v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh Jorginho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ecf neo. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Kante thay v\u00ec ch\u01a1i gi\u0103ng ngang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Barkley g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, th\u00ec Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 do b\u00ean tr\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n d\u00e2ng l\u00ean tham gia th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, N&rsquo;Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho The Blues, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Kante c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi &ldquo;b\u1ed9 n\u00e3o&rdquo; Jorginho, \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhung-diem-nhan-tran-dau-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-0-3-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Chelsea kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nJorginho l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Jorginho l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, hi\u1ebfm khi t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n mang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m s\u1eafc n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Jorginho, Kante ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhi\u1ec1u cho anh. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf Premier League, v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 mong ch\u1edd ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, trong b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho cung co man chao hang tuong doi thanh cong\" title=\"Jorginho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/jorginho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Kepa<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 bom t\u1ea5n Kepa Arrizabalaga trong m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Huddersfield l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, d\u00f9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, Kepa v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 9/8, m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha pressing c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111em l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/kepa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u00ecn chung, Chelsea \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o trong v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, trong khi Morata m\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1edf h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, Huddersfield qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. Nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng theo b\u00e0i v\u1edf g\u00ec, n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Sau nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y &ndash; Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018-172-194267.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018-172-194267.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Huddersfield vs Chelsea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Huddersfield vs Chelsea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2257","checkdouble":"194281"},{"date":"00:10 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt Huddersfield vs Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">802 &ndash; Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League gi\u00e0nh h\u01a1n 800 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (802), v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal (800) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Man United (902).<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Felipe Scolari v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008 (th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Portmouth).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">6 &ndash; Kh\u00f4ng ai s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, v\u1edbi 6/6 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 100%). Kinh ho\u00e0ng hoan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">109 &ndash; Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 109 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 209 tr\u1eadn Premier League. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 69 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 40 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">94 &ndash; \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Jorginho trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong 11 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 &ndash; Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Kante c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi Premier League. Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed7i mua Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2256","checkdouble":"194282"},{"date":"00:47 12/08","title":"H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Hudderfield, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ha-guc-hudderfield-tan-hlv-sarri-danh-loi-khen-cho-mot-cai-ten.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Eden Hazard l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddsfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Pedro ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n 10 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV Sarri cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n copy c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u00e1ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay trong th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y cao t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00ean b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Eden Hazard v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong kho\u1ea3ng 15-20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng&quot; - HLV&nbsp;Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn trong kho\u1ea3ng 15 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. May m\u1eafn cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2, Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec7t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2255","checkdouble":"194283"},{"date":"01:24 12/08","title":"\"Bom t\u1ea5n\" c\u1ee7a Liverpool xo\u00e1y s\u00e2u v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Fabinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fabinho \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb h\u1ecd c\u1ea3. Monaco c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb M.U, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea5p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Monaco nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Liverpool t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Anfield\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Alisson, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" title=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 5 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng quang, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2254","checkdouble":"194284"},{"date":"01:43 12/08","title":"Morata: \"Chelsea v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/morata-chelsea-vua-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194117.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mateo Kovacic</span> t\u1eeb Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho The Blues theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay d\u1edf th\u00ec v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19 anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Alvaro-Morata-phat-bieu-ve-Mateo-Kovacic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata khen ngoi Kovacic\" title=\"Morata khen ng\u1ee3i Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/morata-chelsea-vua-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata khen ng\u1ee3i Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan t\u1ed1t, Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Kovacic, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKovacic l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Kovacic v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1. Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t \u1edf Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2253","checkdouble":"194285"},{"date":"00:57 12/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: N'Golo Kante</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Jorginho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N'Golo Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Kante ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u00fat xa t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t, song anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5&nbsp; v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues nh\u01b0 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kante \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u00fap Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ph\u00fat 34, t\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tung c\u00fa volley hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ben Hamer ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ra s\u00e2n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 34 tr\u1eadn/m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Morata \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata tiep tuc gay that vong\" title=\"Morata ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi Morata: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, t\u00f4i tin khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Alvaro Morata \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, anh ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Willian v\u00e0 Pedro tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Morata l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh ch\u1ec9 tung ra 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p k\u00e9m, Morata \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o tay Giroud ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh v\u00e0 Kante khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Huddersfield g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho co man ra mat NHM rat an tuong\" title=\"Jorginho c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft NHM r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/jofrinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft NHA r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 66 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 94%. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Jorginho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, Jorginho c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Marcos Alonso mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, Jorginho b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League, sau Brian Deane, Alan Thompson, Fabrizio Ravanelli, Peter Kennedy, Adam Le Fondre,&nbsp;Roberto Soldado v\u00e0 Alexandre Pato.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Ross Barkley</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ross Barkley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ef1u sao Everton \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/barker.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Barkley c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n anh ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ea1o ra 1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u sao Everton th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat anh ra ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u1edf ph\u00fat 68. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Barkley c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Loftus-Cheek, Mateo Kovacic ho\u1eb7c Cesc Fabregas.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Terence Kongolo</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Huddersfield t\u1ea1o ra. Terence Kongolo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Terence Kongolo xung dang nhan duoc nhung loi khen ngoi\" title=\"Terence Kongolo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/kologo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Terence Kongolo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb Terence Kongolo ph\u00e1 ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 chia c\u1eaft r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Terence Kongolo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 6 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 Huddersfield th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Khi m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ha-guc-hudderfield-tan-hlv-sarri-danh-loi-khen-cho-mot-cai-ten-172-194283.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</span>, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng sao tr\u1ebb Callum Hudson-Odoi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Pero v\u00e0 Willian thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Callum Hudson-Odoi.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung sao tre cua Chelsea khong co co hoi the hien minh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/odoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i Hazard v\u00e0 Victor Moses l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Hudson-Odoi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Hudson-Odoi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 Ethan Ampadu hay Tammy Abraham c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Gary Cahill v\u00e0 Andreas Christensen, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Ampadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Tammy Abraham c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong sau Morata v\u00e0 Giroud.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2252","checkdouble":"194286"}]}